    <sect3 role="package">
      <title>Introduction to the semantic_version Module</title>

      <para>
        The <application>semantic_version</application> module brings a small
        library to handle the standard for
        <ulink url="http://semver.org/">Semantic Versioning</ulink> in Python.
      </para>

      &lfs130_checked;

