    </sect3>

    <sect3 role="installation">
      <title>Installation of semantic_version</title>

      <para>
        Build the module:
      </para>

&build-wheel;

      <para>
        Now, as the <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem> user:
      </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>&install-wheel; semantic_version</userinput></screen>

      <para>
        To test the installation, run <command>pytest</command>. There are 500+
        warnings issued due to deprecated syntax with newer versions of Python.
      </para>

    </sect3>

